---
description: Section and UI component templates for Silver Studios
globs: src/sections/**/*,src/components/ui/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Sections (`src/sections/**`)

Follow `src/sections/hero/HeroSection.tsx`:

- Types at top, then local sub-components, then default export
- Copy from `@/lib/data`, types from `@/types`
- Server Component unless hooks/events/browser APIs required
- `next/image` for images; semantic `<section>` + headings

# UI (`src/components/ui/**`)

Follow `src/components/ui/Button.tsx`:

- Named export + exported `ComponentNameProps`
- Default values for optional props
- `cn(base, variant, className)` and `{...rest}`
- Export `*Variants()` when links need the same styles

Every file: JSDoc header with `@file` and `@description`.
